    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! It breaks my heart a little to let this beauty go, but it's time for her to find a new home where she'll be as cherished as she was with me. I've kept this gem in absolutely stunning, showroom-ready shape\u2014honestly, she looks and drives like she just rolled off the lot. There might be a tiny, barely-there mark if you really go looking for it, but that\u2019s just a bit of character on an otherwise flawless ride! If you're looking for a vehicle that\u2019s been loved with every single mile, you\u2019ve found it. Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
