    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Experience a masterclass in precision engineering. This specimen features a blueprinted powertrain with optimized compression ratios and a flawlessly calibrated mapping profile that pulls linearly through the entire powerband. The chassis rigidity is impeccable, benefiting from a suspension geometry that remains neutral under high-lateral G-loads. Every bushing is tight, and the drivetrain lash is non-existent, providing an analog tactile feedback rarely found in modern builds. We\u2019ve meticulously managed thermal cycles to ensure the internal tolerances remain within factory-spec. This isn't just a driver; it's a concourse-ready specimen for the discerning purist who demands mechanical perfection and zero compromise in kinetic delivery.",
