    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine gliding through the hills at dusk, the moonlight dancing off a finish so deep it looks like liquid sapphire. This isn't just a car; it's a time machine crafted for the soul. The interior greets you with the rich, unmistakable aroma of hand-stitched leather that has aged like a fine vintage, and every turn of the key is a symphony of precision engineering. It carries the whisper of a thousand adventures yet to be had, standing as a pristine testament to an era where driving was an art form. To own it is to hold a masterpiece of motion, preserved in a state of grace that defies the passing years.",
      "price": 48900.0,
